Package org.jgentleframework.configure.objectmeta

Interface Summary
InClass Represents the Class which is 'target class' of current binding bean.
ObjectAnnotating This interface represents a ObjectAnnotating which be responsible for annotating executing process correspongding to an ID of a Definition which is designated in ObjectBindingConstant .
ObjectAttach<U> This interface represents an ObjectBindingConstant which is responsible for mapping management.
ObjectBindingConstant Represents an ObjectBindingConstant which is responsible for mapping management and injected data controller.
ObjectBindingInterceptor The Interface ObjectBindingInterceptor.
ObjectConstant Represents an ObjectConstant.ScopeObjectConstant.
 

Class Summary
Binder This class manages all necessary information including the meta objects ( ObjectBindingConstant, ObjectAttach, ObjectConstant, ObjectBindingInterceptor, ...) in order to instantiate bean.
InClassImpl The implementation of InClass interface.
ObjectAttach.ScopeObject The Class ScopeObject.
ObjectAttachImpl<T> The implementation of ObjectAttach interface.
ObjectBindingConstant.ScopeObjectBinding The Class ScopeObjectBinding.
ObjectBlock Represents the Block instance.
ObjectConstant.ScopeObjectConstant The Class ScopeObjectConstant.
ObjectConstantImpl This class represents an ObjectConstant specifying dependency mapping to the given unique names.
